<div class="card card-custom gutter-b cb-card cb-admin-card cb-admin-settings-nav-card">
    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="cb-admin-section-kicker">Sekmeli Gezinme</div>
        <div class="cb-admin-section-title">Global settings akisi</div>
        <p class="cb-admin-section-description">Bu sayfa uzun bir dump yerine sekmeli operasyon akisi olarak duzenlendi. Ilk bakista yalnizca gerekli sekme ve ozet gorunur.</p>

        <div class="cb-admin-settings-nav nav nav-pills flex-column mt-5" role="tablist" aria-orientation="vertical">
            <a class="nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link is-active active" id="cb_admin_settings_tab_link_overview" data-toggle="tab" href="#cb_admin_settings_tab_overview" role="tab" aria-controls="cb_admin_settings_tab_overview" aria-selected="true">Genel Durum</a>
            <a class="nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link" id="cb_admin_settings_tab_link_wizard" data-toggle="tab" href="#cb_admin_settings_tab_wizard" role="tab" aria-controls="cb_admin_settings_tab_wizard" aria-selected="false">Kurulum Sihirbazi</a>
            <a class="nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link" id="cb_admin_settings_tab_link_critical" data-toggle="tab" href="#cb_admin_settings_tab_critical" role="tab" aria-controls="cb_admin_settings_tab_critical" aria-selected="false">Kritik Ayarlar</a>
            <a class="nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link" id="cb_admin_settings_tab_link_sync" data-toggle="tab" href="#cb_admin_settings_tab_sync" role="tab" aria-controls="cb_admin_settings_tab_sync" aria-selected="false">Senkronizasyon ve Islemler</a>
            <a class="nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link-danger" id="cb_admin_settings_tab_link_activation" data-toggle="tab" href="#cb_admin_settings_tab_activation" role="tab" aria-controls="cb_admin_settings_tab_activation" aria-selected="false">Aktivasyon</a>
            <a class="nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link" id="cb_admin_settings_tab_link_details" data-toggle="tab" href="#cb_admin_settings_tab_details" role="tab" aria-controls="cb_admin_settings_tab_details" aria-selected="false">Gecmis ve Detaylar</a>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-admin-info-strip cb-admin-info-strip-warning mt-6">
            <div>
                <div class="cb-admin-info-strip-title">Kritik alan ayrimi</div>
                <div class="cb-admin-info-strip-text">Salt okunur snapshot, yazilabilir konfigürasyon ve audit etkili komutlar sekmeler icinde ayri tutulur. Aktivasyon ve emergency yolu ayri sekmede gorunur.</div>
            </div>
            <span class="cb-admin-info-strip-meta">Guarded</span>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-admin-info-strip cb-admin-info-strip-info mt-5">
            <div>
                <div class="cb-admin-info-strip-title">Onerilen akis</div>
                <div class="cb-admin-info-strip-text">Genel Durum ile baslayin, Kurulum Sihirbazi ile eksikleri kapatin, sonra Kritik Ayarlar ve Aktivasyon sekmelerine gecin.</div>
            </div>
            <span class="cb-admin-info-strip-meta">Ops</span>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-admin-inline-actions mt-5">
            <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="ConfigHistory" class="btn btn-light-primary font-weight-bold">Config history</a>
            <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="SystemStateHistory" class="btn btn-light-warning font-weight-bold">State history</a>
            <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="Audit" class="btn btn-primary font-weight-bolder">Audit / trace</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>